  "detailed_description": "This game is developed from the ground up for HTC Vive and it's not game AAA grade.<br />\r\nStep in the midst of a low poly zombie apocalypse. Kill them all and save the town where you growing up.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nReal-life weapon handling: Using VR motion controllers handle over 42 different weapons.<br />\r\nMove where you want: using touchpad you can smoothly go there where you wish.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFew different game mode:<br />\r\n- Throw missions<br />\r\n- Street missions<br />\r\n- Arena missions<br />\r\n(more in next updates)",
